\begin_inset Formula $n_{c}=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\gamma_{i}^{c}$
\end_inset

 be the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

number
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 of points 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

soft assigned
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 to cluster 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

